159
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,480
Here it is?

160
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:41,600
That’s right. It’s said that Bu Le
is active around here at night.

161
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,360
This place is remote.

162
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:46,440
