172
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:49,570
Xiao Wu, you’re such a cute girl.

173
00:16:57,800 --> 00:17:01,230
Come with me. I’ll take you to buy candies.

174
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:05,100
Then I’ll send you home, okay?

175
00:17:05,110 --> 00:17:06,650
Thank you, Uncle.

176
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:14,240
Come with me.

177
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:29,130
Little San, is that really Xiao Wu?

178
00:17:29,130 --> 00:17:31,160
What is she planning?

179
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:33,870
This girl doesn’t change at all.

180
00:17:33,870 --> 00:17:36,060
Let’s follow up. Just in case.

181
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:15,370
Uncle, where is the candy shop?

182
00:18:15,370 --> 00:18:18,580
It’s dark here. I’m a little scared.

183
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:31,900
Little girl, don’t be afraid. I’ll protect you.

184
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:48,040
Uncle, you should protect yourself.

185
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:51,670
